divs: Sighting DetailsWatching the stars on Halloween night, it was cloudless around 8:20, I had just checked the time on my phone a few minutes earlier, I noticed four tightly packed diffusely lit round objects almost touching as if they were one object in a diamond shape craft travelling from the South to the North. It was about as high as the jets fly overhead, higher than the commercial jets that take off and land at MCI. There were no normal lights that signify that it was a commercial flight. I lost sight of it very quickly as the city lights washed out the object. The object was bigger than a commercial jet and was travelling in a straight path faster than a commercial jet.
